      </div>
      <div class="strip-logo-item">
        <img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=figma.com&sz=64" alt="Figma" width="28" height="28" />
        <span>Figma</span>
      </div>
      <div class="strip-logo-item">
        <img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=linear.app&sz=64" alt="Linear" width="28" height="28" />
        <span>Linear</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── Features section ─────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="features-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Capabilities</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">One prompt.<br/>Every app.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Faria sees your screen, understands context, and takes action across your entire workflow — no tab-switching, no copy-paste.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Natural Language Actions</h3>
        <p>Describe what you want in plain English. Faria translates intent into precise actions across any app on your Mac.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Screen Awareness</h3>
        <p>Faria sees what's on your screen and understands context — no need to explain what app you're in or what you're looking at.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Privacy First</h3>
        <p>Everything runs locally on your Mac. Your screen data never leaves your device unless you explicitly approve an action.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Instant Activation</h3>
        <p>One keyboard shortcut summons the command bar. Type your request, hit enter, and Faria handles the rest — anywhere on your Mac.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── How it works ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="how-inner">
    <div class="features-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three steps. Zero friction.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-row">
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>Summon</h3>
        <p>Press <kbd>⌥</kbd> <kbd>Space</kbd> to open the Faria command bar from anywhere.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>Prompt</h3>
        <p>Describe what you need in natural language. Be as specific or vague as you want.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Done</h3>
        <p>Faria acts across your apps — composing emails, scheduling meetings, pulling data — autonomously.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── Final CTA ────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="final-cta-inner">
    <div class="final-cta-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <h2>Stop switching. Start prompting.</h2>
    <p>Get early access to Faria and join the beta.</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/Panchangam18/faria/releases/latest/download/Faria.dmg" class="cta-download cta-download-final">
      <img class="apple-logo" src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/apple-logo.png`} alt="" width="18" height="22" />
      Download for Mac
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

